{"tid":1509460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［第七條人命？］25歲仔財困墮樓　魂斷順天邨","createTime":"2019-08-27T00:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-27T10:32:12.000Z","uid":43785,"like":15,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"97fed28f38c5f4e195ffb6e11743f5113be0722b","tid":1509460,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:26:33.000Z","msg":"25歲仔財困墮樓　魂斷順天邨<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vw5nQQ6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVw5nQQ6.jpg&h=b38550bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190827/mobile/bkn-20190827034931294-0827_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190827%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190827034931294-0827_00822_001.html&d=D7ApRvRekvrpuPbHHlYQrvTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=29ce0480\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190827/mobile/bkn-20190827034931294-0827_00822_001.html</a><br />\n秀茂坪順天邨天韻樓，昨日(26日)晚上9時許，一名男子被發現昏迷倒臥天井上，懷疑由高處墮下，救護員到場經檢查後，證實事主當場死亡。警可方現場未有檢獲遺書，經初步調查，事件並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，事主25歲姓郭，疑因金錢問題困擾萌生死念。<br />\n點知係金錢問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又老屈<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可能係同一個人？？<br />\n<br />\n（緊急）有冇順天村手足？我懷疑我朋友想輕生！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1508484\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1508484</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iTEvZKX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiTEvZKX.jpg&h=7463a22e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6f736831fecb849cf03e1b73aac1b118c9038f41","tid":1509460,"uid":153151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T00:26:46.000Z","